<p>We want to hear your views on these proposals. Your feedback will inform the development of the scheme.</p>
<p>As we are currently unable to hold local events, we have created a virtual reality room to present he next steps for Urmston’s Active Neighbourhood project. By visiting the virtual room you can learn more about the proposals which include statistics of each ward, walking and cycling interventions at specific locations and drawings of what we are proposing.
</p>
